 between having an earth in this mysterious human body you've been given under your own tree of enlightenment.","duration":13.48,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.19608695652173913,0.3933333333333333,0.13445652173913042,0.0375,0.18621739130434783,0.14632608695652172,0.20796735905044508,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.28164965809277265,0.0,0.5841466359084649,0.41859050445103846,0.6016266051502632,0.8265,0.3323902077151335],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":84.18,"end":90.31,"text":"And suggestion is that to help quiet and tanned.","duration":6.13,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.0,0.16166666666666663,0.06,0.11416666666666665,0.0375,0.19433333333333336,0.13599999999999998,0.1901141924959218,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.37693311582381744,0.1,0.8665,0.3270342577487766],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":91.31,"end":94.31,"text":"Most people find it helpful to close their eyes.","duration":3.0,"vector":[0.31622776601683794,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.14777777777777779,0.17943215116604916,0.09194444444444447,0.0375,0.20322222222222222,0.13183333333333333,0.305,0.5,0.0,0.15486832980505139,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.6194321511660492,0.6449999999999999,0.1,0.8665,0.36150000000000004],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":94.31,"end":100.38,"text":"And if that's uncomfortable then you can kind of leave them half open and downcast.","duration":6.07,"vector":[0.5,0.2,0.0,0.16916666666666663,0.185,0.11416666666666665,0.21893233773127296,0.19433333333333336,0.13824999999999998,0.2653377265238882,0.5,0.0,0.335,0.1,0.15,0.16493848884661177,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.5524546952224056,0.323963093307967,0.9864999999999999,0.3496013179571665],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":100.38,"end":106.6,"text":"And bring your attention just to this present moment into your body seated on the earth.","duration":6.22,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.17312499999999997,0.2952941176470588,0.1225,0.0375,0.19100000000000003,0.1394375,0.2729260450160772,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.5701607717041801,0.4318862350044439,0.9664999999999999,0.35187781350482317],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":106.6,"end":134.25,"text":"And as you tune in to this moment into your body, if you notice any obvious tightness or tension that you can easily release, do so.","duration":27.65,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.14596153846153848,0.3562962962962963,0.10903846153846154,0.0375,0.1963846153846154,0.13128846153846152,0.15052441229656421,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.27698003589195014,0.0,0.5,0.28455696202531644,0.5568446086483424,0.7665,0.3151573236889693],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":134.25,"end":142.32,"text":"Let the eyes and face be soft, loosen the jaw.","duration":8.07,"vector":[0.30151134457776363,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.11374999999999999,0.06,0.0875,0.0375,0.20500000000000002,0.12162499999999998,0.1729368029739778,0.5,0.0,0.15045340337332908,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.3368525402726148,0.1,0.8865000000000001,0.3218810408921934],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":142.32,"end":162.93,"text":"If you like, you can roll your head in a circle and release your neck and let it find a simple upright.","duration":20.61,"vector":[0.20851441405707477,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.1052272727272727,0.49341748502846766,0.0,0.0375,0.24000000000000002,0.1190681818181818,0.16005822416302762,0.5,0.0,0.12255432421712242,0.1,0.03531707226860886,0.0,0.2508870971079189,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.3068025230470644,0.6190088831004136,0.85682