t":"And how you can let go and be completely supported by the earth, by the floor, by the chair.","duration":7.67,"vector":[0.0,0.3341640786499874,0.08000000000000002,0.12394736842105263,0.16,0.08960526315789474,0.0375,0.20415789473684212,0.12468421052631579,0.3194544189436973,0.5,0.165939849254992,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.5535071707953054,0.2905126450481774,0.9065000000000001,0.3658363256831092],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":183.86,"end":193.01,"text":"You can rest just where you are.","duration":9.15,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.09142857142857143,0.46,0.0875,0.0375,0.20500000000000002,0.11492857142857142,0.137377049180328,0.5,0.23940140490643416,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.25387978142076534,0.6305825844944186,0.8265,0.3112131147540984],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":193.01,"end":202.54,"text":"Let the belly be soft and the breath natural.","duration":9.53,"vector":[0.6324555320336759,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.13527777777777777,0.06,0.09194444444444447,0.0375,0.20322222222222222,0.12808333333333333,0.1508289611752361,0.5,0.0,0.24973665961010275,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.28526757607555087,0.1,0.8665,0.3152486883525708],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":202.54,"end":218.66,"text":"And let the heart be soft as well to receive whatever arises with a spirit of kindness, compassion.","duration":16.12,"vector":[0.22941573387056174,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.27843296021489133,0.06,0.14750000000000002,0.0375,0.181,0.1710298880644674,0.1637468982630273,0.5,0.0,0.35824045403173027,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.31540942928039695,0.1,0.9265000000000001,0.3191240694789082],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":218.66,"end":238.68,"text":"And now with this embodied presence, begin to pay attention to the miraculous play of experience that arises the thoughts and sounds and feelings and sensations.","duration":20.02,"vector":[0.0,0.31547005383792515,0.08000000000000002,0.2276923076923077,0.06,0.17057692307692307,0.0375,0.31893851709193977,0.1558076923076923,0.2235906189377674,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.3472727272727271,0.1,0.7665,0.33707718568133027],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":238.68,"end":250.96,"text":"Let yourself be present just where you are for the life that moves through you with mindfulness or let's call it loving awareness.","duration":12.28,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.09921990712461867,0.31,0.12576086956521737,0.0375,0.18969565217391307,0.1172659721373856,0.22047231270358306,0.5,0.15426883249885243,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.44776872964169373,0.4341466359084649,0.8265,0.33614169381107495],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":250.96,"end":258.3,"text":"And notice what displays itself as you sit in the present.","duration":7.34,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.16318181818181815,0.22666666666666666,0.12022727272727271,0.0375,0.19190909090909092,0.13645454545454544,0.1923978201634877,0.5,0.20355894486793433,0.06,0.3590750207410073,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.38226158038147123,0.3776988184128126,0.9065000000000001,0.3277193460490463],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":258.3,"end":361.18,"text":"And after just a minute or so, you may notice that the attention wanders from the present planning, remembering imagining, problem-solving, judging, liking, disliking, all different things that take you away from being just here where you are.","duration":102.88,"vector":[-0.15811388300841897,0.2948683298050514,0.08000000000000002,0.2206410256410256,0.21000000000000002,0.09429747059492939,0.08493416490252569,0.20228101176202826,0.15369230769230768,0.1463785138815851,0.5790569415042095,0.12575888928001475,0.06,0.1,0.1816227766016838,0.11432626298183159,0.0625,0.2632455532033676,0.0,0.568595757789099,0.18633942457231725,0.318595757789099,0.5036539501058485,0.32340038714498065],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":361.18,"end":380.77,"text":"So to help deepen the sense of presence, underneath the waves of thoughts and plans and sensations and sounds, become aware of the wave of your breath, how your body is breathing itself.","duration":19.59,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.0,0.16962121212121212,0.17764705882352944,0.11416666666666665,0.0375,0.19433333333333336,0.13838636363636364,0.2063399693721288,0.5,0.13420574976682972,0.06,0.1,0.05567577817162013,0.0,0.17230470435467887,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.4147932618683005,0.290850195059982,0.6349891799645542,0.3507668351773146],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":380.77,"end":396.81,"text":"And feel it is coolness in the nostrils, the upper lip, swirling tingling in the back of the throat, or the rise in fall of chest or belly.","duration":16.04,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.12446428571428572,0.13801211558666523,0.0875,0.0375,0.20500000000000002,0.12483928571428571,0.21092269326683277,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.42548628428927643,0.1,0.7264999999999999,0.3332768079800499],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":396.81,"end":414.98,"text":"And if it's at all difficult to sense the breath, put one hand on your belly and leave it there for this meditation time, and feel the rise and fall of your belly in the palm of your hand.","duration":18.17,"vector":[-0.15811388300841897,0.2948683298050514,0.08000000000000002,0.11487179487179486,0.27859575778909895,0.0875,0.08493416490252569,0.20500000000000002,0.12196153846153845,0.27892696868591693,0.5790569415042095,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.26858541225631427,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.568595757789099,0.49561915244909155,0.318595757789099,0.4958273128969317,0.3457723964553542],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":414.98,"end":427.33,"text":"And feeling each breath in bite a sense of calm or ease to grow, bringing mind and body together with each breath as you breathe in and breathe out.","duration":12.35,"vector":[0.3651483716701107,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.20035726054091868,0.20362803007392744,0.0875,0.0375,0.20500000000000002,0.1476071781622756,0.25611336032388715,0.5,0.0,0.2608316044185609,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.17794204511089118,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.53093117408907,0.3205893934811882,0.7064999999999999,0.34683400809716614],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":427.33,"end":567.43,"text":"And again, after just a minute or two, you notice that frequently the attention moves off of the breath.","duration":140.1,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.17394736842105263,0.16,0.13171052631578947,0.0375,0.1873157894736842,0.13968421052631577,0.09017130620985013,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.15085440841362907,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.14373304782298357,0.2905126450481774,0.9065000000000001,0.29705139186295504],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":567.43,"end":584.97,"text":"When it does, as soon as you wake up, realize that you've gone someplace else, very kindly, almost as if to say thank you for the diversion, bring your attention back to the next breath.","duration":17.54,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.07583333333333334,0.28222222222222226,0.09321428571428574,0.0375,0.2027142857142857,0.11024999999999999,0.2296579247434429,0.5,0.13117216576798174,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.11924742342543794,0.22982268108289416,0.2,0.3333333333333333,0.5,0.46920182440136676,0.46531913033274774,0.5865,0.4388973774230329],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":584.97,"end":589.29,"text":"It's the very returning to this breath.","duration":4.32,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.16464285714285715,0.06,0.10464285714285716,0.0375,0.19814285714285715,0.13689285714285715,0.20152777777777958,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.403564814814819,0.1,0.8265,0.33045833333333385],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":589.29,"end":604.06,"text":"Just as it is, the coming back that starts to cultivate this power of mindful loving awareness that brings you more and more deeply here into the present.","duration":14.77,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.17284766908852595,0.1740178571428571,0.12896551724137933,0.12607142857142856,0.0375,0.18957142857142859,0.13970535714285712,0.22218009478673004,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.45175355450237004,0.24697763282804455,0.7264999999999999,0.336654028436019],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":604.06,"end":634.33,"text":"No judgment, just as simple return, as each time you come back, this breath, and in bite a sense of ease, or calm to grow with every breath you feel.","duration":30.27,"vector":[0.3592106040535498,0.30776318121606494,0.08000000000000002,0.11249999999999999,0.26499079257614866,0.0875,0.0375,0.20500000000000002,0.12125,0.19743629329911158,0.5898026510133875,0.0,0.16776318121606493,0.1,0.05121708388527378,0.0,0.17643780176744886,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.293439048562933,0.3049907925761487,0.6953904624503253,0.3669480014153562],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":634.33,"end":715.82,"text":"This breath, this breath, ease and calm, and guided, as it comes in, ease and calm and guided, as you breathe out.","duration":81.49,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.12113636363636365,0.14695652173913043,0.0875,0.0375,0.20500000000000002,0.12384090909090908,0.10024788317584982,0.5,0.0,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.0625,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.16724506074364953,0.2725479198110764,0.8465,0.30007436495275497],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":715.82,"end":874.88,"text":"One more instruction that can be helpful, as you've been sensing the breath, the other sounds, thoughts and sensations, horizon fall around the breath like waves of the ocean, with the breath in the center of the moll.","duration":159.06,"vector":[0.16012815380508713,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.17296052631578945,0.18057601620844035,0.043863383419289734,0.0375,0.22245464663228412,0.13938815789473682,0.0979177668804225,0.5,0.0,0.10803844614152613,0.1,0.15,0.0,0.33038189477916724,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.1618081227209858,0.1512820512820513,0.5265,0.29937533006412675],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":874.88,"end":892.87,"text":"But periodically one of the waves will become strong, a strong sensation allowed sound, a compelling thought, and really pull your attention away from the breath.","duration":17.99,"vector":[0.19245008972987526,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.21663461538461537,0.21434823025009714,0.06858976731386385,0.0375,0.21256409307445448,0.1524903846153846,0.18839355197331847,0.5962250448649375,0.0,0.11773502691896257,0.28730636441072044,0.2558475493514314,0.20879026029337178,0.0625,0.2,0.19245008972987526,0.5,0.37291828793774306,0.2543482302500971,0.7569737205583711,0.38232859161365934],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":892.87,"end":911.49,"text":"When this happens, let go of the focus on the breath and receive the thinking or the emotion or the sound, whatever it is, with the same loving awareness,","duration":18.62,"vector":[0.0,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.16698275862068962,0.06,0.13025862068965516,0.0375,0.18789655172413794,0.1375948275862069,0.19680988184747583,0.5,0.14109583291331143,0.06,0.1,0.15,0.12826893901