y","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":943.07,"end":960.97,"text":"or calm and happy, whatever it happens to be, give it space to be present, and when that wave passes or you are at ease with it, then return back to the breath.","duration":17.9,"vector":[0.17149858514250882,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.12,0.11882352941176472,0.0875,0.0375,0.20500000000000002,0.1235,0.2182681564245812,0.5,0.13420574976682972,0.11144957554275264,0.1,0.15,0.24401045412150857,0.17230470435467887,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.44262569832402276,0.23202666564821728,0.6265,0.33548044692737433],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kappa","tau"]},{"source":"Jack Kornfield Guided Meditation_ Coming Back Home To Yourself__watch","speaker":"Ram Dass","start":960.97,"end":974.98,"text":"So you're either here with this breath or with a loving awareness, you acknowledge a strong wave when it's present that's carried your attention.","duration":14.01,"vector":[0.2,0.2,0.08000000000000002,0.20229166666666665,0.3,0.13916666666666666,0.0375,0.18433333333333335,0.14818749999999997,0.2084796573875804,0.5,0.15177026276073363,0.12,0.1,0.03999999999999998,0.13797296614612148,0.18667566953150933,0.2,0.0,0.5,0.41978586723768757,0.5055675593753457,0.8164,0.3545438972162741],"dim_names":["valence","arousal","dominance","topic_depth","rapport","formality","vulnerability","playfulness","intellectual","momentum","certainty","curiosity","warmth","surprise","tension","narrative","metaphor","agency","temporal_focus","scope","pace","reciprocity","kap